data.description: Come discover this waterfront beauty with a spacious open floor plan is accentuated by diagonal tile in all the living areas and new 8 x 24 tile in the bedrooms. The kitchen boasts 42-inch cabinets, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, movable island, and a pass-through window. The den, off the kitchen that is perfect for an office and large enough to accommodate guests. The primary bedroom has views of the lake, spacious walk-in closet/extra shelving, double vanities, soaking tub, and large shower. Morning sunrises and evening stargazing can be caught on the screened in patio with extended paver sundeck. You will feel safe and secure knowing the windows are all protected with accordion shutters. Great community, with tons of activities and prime location.
